displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Chandigarh, India.

labels.name: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

highlights.text: Arjan Dhillon has the most spots on Top Songs Chandigarh. “25-25” is the highest at #2.
“Excuses” by AP Dhillon, Gurinder Gill, and Intense has been on Top Songs Chandigarh the longest, at 57 weeks straight.
“Trucker” by Arjan Dhillon is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chandigarh, up 68 spots at #16.
“High Life” by Jass Bajwa is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chandigarh at #55.
